Echo server using java.util.concurrent package
==============================================

How to build with maven 3
=========================
1. cd to Networking dir
2. mvn clean install

How to start the Server
=======================
1. cd target
2. java -cp com.github.networking-1.0.0.jar com.github.networking.server.Server

How to start the Client
=======================
1. cd target
2. java -cp com.github.networking-1.0.0.jar com.github.networking.client.Client C1